{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01WD45hoXQXmmkRUbGn7QwXN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me look at the actual log file to understand the format. But first, let me understand the current issue.\n\nLooking at the progress reporter code (lines 177-211):\n\n1. The current code uses `LAST_LOG_LINES` to track progress by line count\n2. It uses `jq` to parse stream-json, selecting `content_block_delta` events and extracting `.event.delta.text`\n\nWait, looking more carefully at the current code (lines 199-203), it seems like the jq parsing is already there for stream-json. The issue description says \"reporter 用 tail + sed + grep 处理日志，所有 JSON 行都被当成不可读内容过滤掉了\" but the current code actually has jq.\n\n\nLet me re-examine the actual stream-json format. The jq filter is checking for `type==\"stream_event\"` and `event.type==\"content_block_delta\"`, which should work for the documented format. But with `--include-partial-messages`, the event structure might differ from what the filter expects, or there could be other event types being generated that aren't being captured.\n\nThe real issue is likely the deduplication logic—if the log file grows but the line count stays the same after the first read, the script would skip processing. I should switch to tracking byte offsets instead of line counts, and also truncate the log snippet to 200 characters to avoid overwhelming output. Let me check the actual stream format and update the parsing logic accordingly. Looking at the Anthropic API documentation, the `content_block_delta` event structure has `delta.type` set to `\"text_delta\"` and the actual text in `delta.text`, so my jq filter should be targeting the right path. The real problem might be that invalid JSON lines or stderr output is getting mixed into the stream, causing jq to fail silently. Let me focus on what the user actually needs: handling multiple event types properly and switching the dedup strategy to work with the actual message content.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3776,"cache_read_input_tokens":17163,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3776},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"11eb47d5-9abd-4672-b0fd-3531b749ab95","uuid":"653d4c02-a0b8-4fcf-8042-e5915798cea2"}
