{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012kJRaReXW7VRq4s6h7q3gJ","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→---\n     2→name: clawclau\n     3→description: 'ClawClau v1.3.0 — The ONLY authorized way to dispatch Claude Code tasks. Spawns Claude Code in isolated tmux sessions with automatic background monitoring, completion notification, and optional real-time progress reporting. NOT for: interactive Claude Code sessions or environments without tmux/claude/jq.'\n     4→metadata:\n     5→  {\n     6→    \"openclaw\":\n     7→      {\n     8→        \"emoji\": \"🦞\",\n     9→        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"tmux\", \"jq\", \"claude\"] },\n    10→        \"install\":\n    11→          [\n    12→            { \"id\": \"tmux\", \"kind\": \"brew\", \"package\": \"tmux\" },\n    13→            { \"id\": \"jq\", \"kind\": \"brew\", \"package\": \"jq\" },\n    14→            {\n    15→              \"id\": \"claude\",\n    16→              \"kind\": \"npm\",\n    17→              \"package\": \"@anthropic-ai/claude-code\",\n    18→              \"bins\": [\"claude\"],\n    19→            },\n    20→          ],\n    21→      },\n    22→  }\n    23→---\n    24→\n    25→# ClawClau v1.3.0 — Claude Code 唯一调度方式\n    26→\n    27→小八调度 Claude Code 的唯一合法方式。通过 tmux 隔离会话派发任务，自动启动后台 monitor，任务完成后自动通知。\n    28→\n    29→## When to Use\n    30→\n    31→**所有** Claude Code 任务都必须通过 ClawClau 派发（`exec` 调用 `claude-spawn.sh`）。\n    32→\n    33→**绝对禁止**：\n    34→- ❌ `exec` 直接调用 `claude -p`（会超时挂死）\n    35→- ❌ `sessions_spawn` + `runtime: \"acp\"`（ACP 已弃用）\n    36→\n    37→Do NOT use for:\n    38→- Tasks requiring real-time streaming output\n    39→- Environments without tmux, jq, or Claude Code\n    40→\n    41→## First-Time Setup\n    42→\n    43→```bash\n    44→# Set up the working directory\n    45→export CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\"\n    46→mkdir -p \"$CLAWCLAU_HOME/logs\"\n    47→echo '[]' > \"$CLAWCLAU_HOME/active-tasks.json\"\n    48→```\n    49→\n    50→Add to shell profile for persistence:\n    51→```bash\n    52→echo 'export CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\"' >> ~/.zshrc\n    53→```\n    54→\n    55→## Configuration\n    56→\n    57→| Variable | Default | Description |\n    58→|----------|---------|-------------|\n    59→| `CLAWCLAU_HOME` | `~/.clawclau` | Base directory for registry and logs |\n    60→| `CLAWCLAU_SHELL` | `bash` | Shell for launching Claude Code in tmux |\n    61→\n    62→## Scripts\n    63→\n    64→All scripts are in `scripts/` relative to this skill directory. Set `CLAWCLAU_HOME` before calling.\n    65→\n    66→### Spawn a task\n    67→\n    68→```bash\n    69→CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-spawn.sh <task-id> \"<prompt>\" [workdir] [timeout-seconds] [--interval <seconds>]\n    70→```\n    71→\n    72→- `<task-id>`: alphanumeric + dash/underscore only\n    73→- `<prompt>`: the task for Claude Code\n    74→- `[workdir]`: defaults to current directory\n    75→- `[timeout-seconds]`: defaults to 600 (10 min)\n    76→- `[--interval <seconds>]`: optional — enable progress reporting every N seconds (default: off)\n    77→\n    78→Example (no progress):\n    79→```bash\n    80→CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-spawn.sh \"refactor-auth\" \\\n    81→  \"Refactor src/auth.ts to use JWT tokens instead of sessions\" \\\n    82→  \"$HOME/my-project\" 300\n    83→```\n    84→\n    85→Example (with progress reports every 60 seconds):\n    86→```bash\n    87→CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-spawn.sh \"long-task\" \\\n    88→  \"Analyze and rewrite all tests in the project\" \\\n    89→  \"$HOME/my-project\" 1800 --interval 60\n    90→```\n    91→\n    92→Progress notifications are sent via `openclaw system event` with format:\n    93→```\n    94→[进度] 任务 <id>: 已运行 X 分钟，日志最新输出：<last few lines>\n    95→```\n    96→ANSI escape codes are stripped. If there is no new log content since the last report, the notification is skipped (dedup).\n    97→\n    98→### Check task status\n    99→\n   100→```bash\n   101→CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-check.sh [task-id]\n   102→```\n   103→\n   104→Without argument: lists all tasks. With argument: shows details + last output.\n   105→\n   106→### Get results\n   107→\n   108→```bash\n   109→CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-result.sh <task-id>\n   110→```\n   111→\n   112→### Monitor (auto-detect completion)\n   113→\n   114→```bash\n   115→CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-monitor.sh\n   116→```\n   117→\n   118→Set up cron for automatic monitoring:\n   119→```bash\n   120→# crontab -e\n   121→*/2 * * * * CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" /path/to/skills/clawclau/scripts/claude-monitor.sh\n   122→```\n   123→\n   124→### Kill a task\n   125→\n   126→```bash\n   127→CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-kill.sh <task-id>\n   128→```\n   129→\n   130→### Steer a running task\n   131→\n   132→```bash\n   133→CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-steer.sh <task-id> \"<message>\"\n   134→```\n   135→\n   136→Note: steering only works with interactive Claude Code sessions, not `claude -p`.\n   137→\n   138→## Task Lifecycle\n   139→\n   140→```\n   141→running → done     (tmux ended, log has content)\n   142→running → failed   (tmux ended, log empty)\n   143→running → timeout  (exceeded timeout)\n   144→running → killed   (manually terminated)\n   145→```\n   146→\n   147→## v1.3.0 Key Features\n   148→\n   149→- **spawn 自动启动后台 monitor**：无需手动 cron，`claude-spawn.sh` 完成后自动在后台运行 `claude-monitor.sh`\n   150→- **完成自动通知**：monitor 检测到任务结束后自动执行 `openclaw system event --mode now`\n   151→- **数据目录**：`~/.clawclau/`（active-tasks.json + logs/ + prompts/）\n   152→- **进度汇报**（v1.2.0 新增，v1.3.0 修复）：`--interval <秒数>` 参数启动后台进度 reporter，定期读取日志最新内容并发送通知；自动去重（日志无新内容则跳过）；自动剥除 ANSI 转义码\n   153→- **stream-json 实时日志**（v1.3.0 修复）：wrapper 改用 `--output-format stream-json`，claude 主动逐行 flush 每个 API 事件到 stdout，日志文件实时写入，进度 reporter 可在任务运行中检测到新行\n   154→\n   155→### v1.3.0 Bug Fix: 进度汇报实时性\n   156→\n   157→**根因**：旧 wrapper 用 `claude -p --output-format text ... 2>&1 | tee logfile`。`claude -p` 等待整个 API 响应生成完毕后才一次性写入 stdout（无论管道还是 PTY），整个任务结束前日志文件始终为 0 bytes。进度 reporter 检测到行数无变化，一直跳过通知。\n   158→\n   159→**排查过的方案**（均不奏效）：\n   160→- `script -q logfile bash -c '...'`：macOS BSD `script` 自身缓冲写入，子进程退出才 flush 文件\n   161→- `tmux pipe-pane`：PTY 让 claude 行缓冲，但 claude -p 在 API 返回前根本不写任何输出，pipe-pane 无法捕获中间内容\n   162→\n   163→**最终修复**：wrapper 改用 `--verbose --output-format stream-json --include-partial-messages`。claude 用此模式逐个 API token 以 JSON 事件行形式 flush 到 stdout，tee 可在任务运行中实时收到数据。进度 reporter 用 `jq` 提取 `content_block_delta.event.delta.text` 生成可读摘要。日志格式为 NDJSON，`claude-result.sh` 从 `result` 事件提取最终文本。\n   164→\n   165→## Security\n   166→\n   167→`claude-spawn.sh` uses `--dangerously-skip-permissions`. Only use in trusted environments.\n   168→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"11eb47d5-9abd-4672-b0fd-3531b749ab95","uuid":"2bdaba59-2187-4090-9798-a3db5dcbbae1","timestamp":"2026-03-19T08:22:16.804Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/yjj/.openclaw/workspace/skills/clawclau/SKILL.md","content":"---\nname: clawclau\ndescription: 'ClawClau v1.3.0 — The ONLY authorized way to dispatch Claude Code tasks. Spawns Claude Code in isolated tmux sessions with automatic background monitoring, completion notification, and optional real-time progress reporting. NOT for: interactive Claude Code sessions or environments without tmux/claude/jq.'\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"🦞\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"tmux\", \"jq\", \"claude\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            { \"id\": \"tmux\", \"kind\": \"brew\", \"package\": \"tmux\" },\n            { \"id\": \"jq\", \"kind\": \"brew\", \"package\": \"jq\" },\n            {\n              \"id\": \"claude\",\n              \"kind\": \"npm\",\n              \"package\": \"@anthropic-ai/claude-code\",\n              \"bins\": [\"claude\"],\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawClau v1.3.0 — Claude Code 唯一调度方式\n\n小八调度 Claude Code 的唯一合法方式。通过 tmux 隔离会话派发任务，自动启动后台 monitor，任务完成后自动通知。\n\n## When to Use\n\n**所有** Claude Code 任务都必须通过 ClawClau 派发（`exec` 调用 `claude-spawn.sh`）。\n\n**绝对禁止**：\n- ❌ `exec` 直接调用 `claude -p`（会超时挂死）\n- ❌ `sessions_spawn` + `runtime: \"acp\"`（ACP 已弃用）\n\nDo NOT use for:\n- Tasks requiring real-time streaming output\n- Environments without tmux, jq, or Claude Code\n\n## First-Time Setup\n\n```bash\n# Set up the working directory\nexport CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\"\nmkdir -p \"$CLAWCLAU_HOME/logs\"\necho '[]' > \"$CLAWCLAU_HOME/active-tasks.json\"\n```\n\nAdd to shell profile for persistence:\n```bash\necho 'export CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\"' >> ~/.zshrc\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\n| Variable | Default | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `CLAWCLAU_HOME` | `~/.clawclau` | Base directory for registry and logs |\n| `CLAWCLAU_SHELL` | `bash` | Shell for launching Claude Code in tmux |\n\n## Scripts\n\nAll scripts are in `scripts/` relative to this skill directory. Set `CLAWCLAU_HOME` before calling.\n\n### Spawn a task\n\n```bash\nCLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-spawn.sh <task-id> \"<prompt>\" [workdir] [timeout-seconds] [--interval <seconds>]\n```\n\n- `<task-id>`: alphanumeric + dash/underscore only\n- `<prompt>`: the task for Claude Code\n- `[workdir]`: defaults to current directory\n- `[timeout-seconds]`: defaults to 600 (10 min)\n- `[--interval <seconds>]`: optional — enable progress reporting every N seconds (default: off)\n\nExample (no progress):\n```bash\nCLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-spawn.sh \"refactor-auth\" \\\n  \"Refactor src/auth.ts to use JWT tokens instead of sessions\" \\\n  \"$HOME/my-project\" 300\n```\n\nExample (with progress reports every 60 seconds):\n```bash\nCLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-spawn.sh \"long-task\" \\\n  \"Analyze and rewrite all tests in the project\" \\\n  \"$HOME/my-project\" 1800 --interval 60\n```\n\nProgress notifications are sent via `openclaw system event` with format:\n```\n[进度] 任务 <id>: 已运行 X 分钟，日志最新输出：<last few lines>\n```\nANSI escape codes are stripped. If there is no new log content since the last report, the notification is skipped (dedup).\n\n### Check task status\n\n```bash\nCLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-check.sh [task-id]\n```\n\nWithout argument: lists all tasks. With argument: shows details + last output.\n\n### Get results\n\n```bash\nCLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-result.sh <task-id>\n```\n\n### Monitor (auto-detect completion)\n\n```bash\nCLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-monitor.sh\n```\n\nSet up cron for automatic monitoring:\n```bash\n# crontab -e\n*/2 * * * * CLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" /path/to/skills/clawclau/scripts/claude-monitor.sh\n```\n\n### Kill a task\n\n```bash\nCLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-kill.sh <task-id>\n```\n\n### Steer a running task\n\n```bash\nCLAWCLAU_HOME=\"$HOME/.clawclau\" ./scripts/claude-steer.sh <task-id> \"<message>\"\n```\n\nNote: steering only works with interactive Claude Code sessions, not `claude -p`.\n\n## Task Lifecycle\n\n```\nrunning → done     (tmux ended, log has content)\nrunning → failed   (tmux ended, log empty)\nrunning → timeout  (exceeded timeout)\nrunning → killed   (manually terminated)\n```\n\n## v1.3.0 Key Features\n\n- **spawn 自动启动后台 monitor**：无需手动 cron，`claude-spawn.sh` 完成后自动在后台运行 `claude-monitor.sh`\n- **完成自动通知**：monitor 检测到任务结束后自动执行 `openclaw system event --mode now`\n- **数据目录**：`~/.clawclau/`（active-tasks.json + logs/ + prompts/）\n- **进度汇报**（v1.2.0 新增，v1.3.0 修复）：`--interval <秒数>` 参数启动后台进度 reporter，定期读取日志最新内容并发送通知；自动去重（日志无新内容则跳过）；自动剥除 ANSI 转义码\n- **stream-json 实时日志**（v1.3.0 修复）：wrapper 改用 `--output-format stream-json`，claude 主动逐行 flush 每个 API 事件到 stdout，日志文件实时写入，进度 reporter 可在任务运行中检测到新行\n\n### v1.3.0 Bug Fix: 进度汇报实时性\n\n**根因**：旧 wrapper 用 `claude -p --output-format text ... 2>&1 | tee logfile`。`claude -p` 等待整个 API 响应生成完毕后才一次性写入 stdout（无论管道还是 PTY），整个任务结束前日志文件始终为 0 bytes。进度 reporter 检测到行数无变化，一直跳过通知。\n\n**排查过的方案**（均不奏效）：\n- `script -q logfile bash -c '...'`：macOS BSD `script` 自身缓冲写入，子进程退出才 flush 文件\n- `tmux pipe-pane`：PTY 让 claude 行缓冲，但 claude -p 在 API 返回前根本不写任何输出，pipe-pane 无法捕获中间内容\n\n**最终修复**：wrapper 改用 `--verbose --output-format stream-json --include-partial-messages`。claude 用此模式逐个 API token 以 JSON 事件行形式 flush 到 stdout，tee 可在任务运行中实时收到数据。进度 reporter 用 `jq` 提取 `content_block_delta.event.delta.text` 生成可读摘要。日志格式为 NDJSON，`claude-result.sh` 从 `result` 事件提取最终文本。\n\n## Security\n\n`claude-spawn.sh` uses `--dangerously-skip-permissions`. Only use in trusted environments.\n","numLines":168,"startLine":1,"totalLines":168}}}
